I love Ghost. Right now, second to [[Red_Bull]], they are my favorite brand
doing it. Consistently they churn out amazing flavors, all with zero sugar,
which is nice. Red Bull fills a different niche for me as their zero-sugar
flavors are fine but their full-sugar offerings are amazing. I only enjoy them
when I am aiming to eat at a caloric surplus. I can enjoy Ghost anytime without
compromising my [[fitness goals|Physical_Fitness]].

